name: Duck in a bag
description:
I couldn't sleep. So I drew this.

My sleep schedule is already messed up. I always tell people about how important it is to eat well and sleep well. I even said that sleeping is the best reset method for all your worries (or at least most of them). But Insomnia has never really leaved my side.

I hope you sleep well and wake up feeling fresh in the morning!
Good night all.
